 taunt works a ton.  I actually like having knights in the group because they can build up agro fast with a stun or tap and then I can piggy back and use that agro when I taunt to top him and get a huge agro boost.  A warrior has nothing that gives him raw agro unless he has EB weapons and such, so we are slow to build on agro sometimes.  I need a few solid rounds to get a good deal of it.  *Sometimes* my slower takes a round or 2, but its never anything serious.  So take your knights if you want, but have fun killing a lot slower and having to heal more!  Ill enjoy my faster exp =) <p>Love<br>
