Really I think in xp grouping that its a hard choice between a pally and a warrior.  Do you want more group utility and better agro from a pally, or do you want more damage output and better tanking skills from a warrior.  To me this is what proves that pallies and warriors are fairly well balanced, the fact that they each have tradeoffs. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=179608">Gartuff</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> &lt;Ex Tempore&gt;<br>
